&lt;p&gt;The Head and Neck, Breast and Dermatology Care Group are looking for an enthusiastic and self-motivated person to work in an administrative capacity to support the Surgical Management team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will work alongside the existing Care group Administrator/ PA assisting with their workload and supporting everyday office tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The essential requirements of this post are a minimum of 6 months previous experience in a administrative post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be educated to GCSE level or equivalent experience in maths and English. Excellent IT skills are essential, with good experience of Microsoft office and excel data entry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Previous applicants need not apply.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
